Definition: feeling or showing worry or solicitude
Example: concerned parents of youthful offenders; was concerned about the future; we feel concerned about accomplishing the task at hand; greatly concerned not to disappoint a small child
Synonyms: UNCONCERNED, ATTENTIVE, TROUBLED, feeling, or, showing, worry, solicitude, concerned, parents, of, youthful, offenders, was, about, the, future, we, feel, accomplishing, task, at, hand, greatly, not, to, disappoint, a, small, child
Category: adj.all
